### Logout
# @name login
GET {{url}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Enemies Api
### get all enemies
# @name enemies
GET {{url}}/api/enemies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### add enemy
POST {{url}}/api/enemies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "Dfdf"
}

### delete enemy
DELETE {{url}}/api/enemies/{{enemyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}